<br>
Hippolyte had already received word of Solari's return.  The guard had recognized the elder from her years in Themiscrya.  With respect, Marpe had went to let Hippolyte know.  And that the travel weary Solari had gone directly to her old hut.<br>
<br>
Hippolyte felt a warm and peaceful feeling at Solari's return.  The once Queen from the Caucaus Mountains had been an important part of Themiscrya from even when she ruled so far away.  Then the day the amazon moved to Themiscrya brought great pride to Hippolyte.<br>
<br>
As her brown eyes danced towards her hut as the mare neared it.  Hippolyte could see the small group.  She slid off the mare and walked up to them.  Quickly saluting Solari by clinking her bracers.  "Yasoo, athelfi!!!" <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
