 &quot; Del, a celebration does sound nice, it has been a long time since I was part of one. But you know I have never been one to attract attention to myself. Some of the new amazons, I dont think know who i am really. So, I really dont know what to do or what to say.&quot; <br>
~ Solari chuckled softly in her own way when she was uneasy or unsure of something. That was her way of dealing with things. Almost always serious, Solari kept herself in the shadows, but always quick to depense of troublemakers with words or with weapons. The older amazons knew how well she could fight and always liked her challenges and fair sportmanship. The days of old were gone, Solari really didnt have to prove herself anymore. She would welcome any questions that came her way.~<br>
